Program is to delete a single selected (by parameter) SCHT row and
the corresponding STCY rows, provided that there are no invoices
present for this schedule.
Note: Logically deleted invoices are still considered to be present.
Any required Error messages are to be sent from calling program(s).
no SCHI rows, no active user simple are you sure? (Y/N)
SCHI rows, no active user confirm with warning (Y/N)
Active user, error (Ok)
Recheck if delete allowed (user may not respond promptly)
SCHT_WAITFORDOCUMENT = 'Y' delete is always allowed
no SCHI, simple are you sure? (Y/N)
SCHI rows, confirm with warning (Y/N)
Note delete always allowed, but situation may have changed
(Schedule may be booked /confirmed then it is no longer wait for doc)
